mist-game-preset-name = The Mist
mist-game-preset-description = The Mist is coming, monsters are crawling out!
    You need to be very careful — the further you go, the more monsters appear on the surface.
    They can appear in the most unexpected places.
    The helicopter pilot will try to help by delivering supplies, but they may not be enough.
    You need to come up with a defensive strategy.
    And remember: whoever wanders too far from Silent Town at night is lost forever.

mist-rules-text =
    The Mist is coming!
    How to enter the game:
    Join the game as a ghost, in actions you can see an action "Join Queue". Press it.
    The map must be clear of monsters, then your character can join other survivors.
    Survivors should kill every monster, because after some time difficulty will increase drastically.
    And remember: "Don't trust anyone!"

mist-player-lifetime = { $character } - from { $start } to { $end } / { $lifetime }
mist-player-death-environment = Couldn't withstand the environment.
mist-player-death-suicide = We remember you, friend...
mist-player-death-player = Made a mistake in choosing a friend.
mist-player-death-player-1 = THANK YOU, "ALLY" { $player }
mist-player-death-monster = Found death in a fight with { $monster }
mist-player-death-unknown = Nobody knows how or when. The developer doesn't either.
